      "text": "はい。新年の大型特番で司会をするのは、初めてですし\n万全の体調で本番に臨みます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It’s my first time hosting a major New Year’s special.\nI’ll be in perfect condition for the real thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.699996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "来年は、私達TRINITYAiLEにとって\n挑戦の年になりそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like the next year will be\na year of challenges for TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.0333301543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
