      "text": "そうですね、2.5次元舞台はいい経験になりました\n優とすみれと一緒に、三人で一皮剥けた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true—the 2.5D stage play was a great experience.\nThe three of us—Yu‚ Sumire‚ and I—really grew from it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.0666634876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 259.3652698835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
