      "text": "優の意外な一面が見れたのも、少し嬉しかったです\nなんでもそつなくこなすイメージがあったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing an unexpected side of Yu made me happy too.\nI always thought she handled everything effortlessly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.6666777292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
